                <ul class="profile-policy__privacy-item-desc-list profile-policy__privacy--flex">
                  <li>Customers may select in-store pickup at checkout. A notification will be sent via email or SMS when the order is ready for collection.</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li>
              <h3 class="profile-policy__privacy-item">
                <span class="profile-policy__privacy-item-no">02</span>
                Pickup Hours
              </h3>
