                <p>Pick-up is available during standard business hours</p>
                <ul class="profile-policy__privacy-item-desc-list">
                  <li>Monday–Thursday: 10:00 AM – 6:00 PM</li>
                  <li>Sunday: 11:00 AM – 5:00 PM</li>
                  <li>Friday: 10:00 AM – 1:00 PM</li>
                  <li>We are closed on Saturdays.</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li>
              <h3 class="profile-policy__privacy-item">
                <span class="profile-policy__privacy-item-no">03</span>
                Required at Pickup
