                <ul class="profile-policy__privacy-item-desc-list profile-policy__privacy--flex">
                  <li>Please present your order confirmation and a valid government-issued photo ID. If an alternate party is collecting your order, they must provide the order number and the purchaser’s full name.</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </li>
